data.description: Take a look at this charming 3 Bedroom 2 Bath townhome located in the Heart of Lakelands Shopping district. Just off of the famous Wedgewood's golf course and Carpenters way, you find it easy to access shopping, I-4, and a myriad of restaurants. This home boasts 1,602 sq. ft. of living space with stainless steel appliances and wood laminate floors throughout. This gated community offers a club house and pool for enjoyment at your leisure. Schedule a showing today!
